+ Request Invalid parameters (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Basic cmVub3RpZmljYXRpb246dThyZCZkNFkzTjQyOXpXMyRRKD1YOGJL

    + Body

            {
                "mobile_number": "+380939523746"
